{"data":[{"id":563798883,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563798883","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-5f4013c860615f87338ee9b22d1bb5b0_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546278928,"updated_time":1546281452,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e承认别人厉害就这么难吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e高中生就不可能证明哥德巴赫猜想吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就是因为这件事的轰动效应，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主被外星人抓走了！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2019年最伟大的证明就这么消失了！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可惜啊可惜！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e天妒英才！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3a96ee8a23b4fac85f8cb8f6535617a2_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3a96ee8a23b4fac85f8cb8f6535617a2_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3a96ee8a23b4fac85f8cb8f6535617a2_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2248'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2248\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3a96ee8a23b4fac85f8cb8f6535617a2_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3a96ee8a23b4fac85f8cb8f6535617a2_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3a96ee8a23b4fac85f8cb8f6535617a2_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561490325,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"41c5a8abba234a80fb4702054e2e921b","url_token":"mo-ji-zhi-67-37","name":"莫几知","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2e8911295cca2cf122931620940ed029_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2e8911295cca2cf122931620940ed029_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/41c5a8abba234a80fb4702054e2e921b","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561490325","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545972148,"updated_time":1545979117,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":15,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2019年1月1日，两篇神秘的论文分别寄到清华北大数学系主任办公室。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月2日上午，清华北大数学系临时决定停课。下午，清华北大数学教授集中开会，内容无人知晓。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月10日，清华校长预言，今年会发生一件大事。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月20日，清华北大数学系联合邀请世界著名数学家来华交流\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月21日，数学家Alex发表言论:这帮中国人都是疯子，我宁可相信费马有一个美妙的证法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1月25日，数学家Александр说:哥德巴赫如果知道这件事，他会高兴地从棺材里爬出来\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3月27日，哥德巴赫猜想的证明公开\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4月3日，知乎某著名数学爱好者M声称发现了一个致命的错误，引起知乎广泛讨论\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4月8日，哈佛大学，牛津大学，耶鲁大学，麻省理工等各大高校聘请中国一高中生为终身教授(经评论区提醒，应是终生教授)。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e该高中生回应，那我能保送清华北大吗\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560474011,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aea5bb74cdc9c44e0b2b6a450a870459","url_token":"zhi-zhang-shao-nian-55-68","name":"起个名真费劲","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aea5bb74cdc9c44e0b2b6a450a870459","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560474011","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545840654,"updated_time":1545840898,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":49,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管题主是否证明出了哥德巴赫猜想，都会有人支持你，因为谁没年少轻狂过，你还年轻，有的是可能，有的是时间。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你的证明正确，皆大欢喜，如果你的证明不正确，希望你也不要放弃对数学的热爱，毕竟冰冷的高山，不是那么好爬。愿你以后再回想当初的自己，能不悔当初，一笑了之\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e来自一个知乎小透明的首次长(？)答\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e求轻喷\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感激不尽\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561411006,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bbf04340aef5809fbe75adc27a19e46d","url_token":"xin-zhao-de-shui-li-bo-shi","name":"赜实先生","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f9cc23903f4fda215a6e0653d170fec3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f9cc23903f4fda215a6e0653d170fec3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bbf04340aef5809fbe75adc27a19e4